OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F422A1776856004
OL,3,CNHS trust removes advice to give
OL,4,Cchildren Wotsits, Skips and Cadbury
OL,5,CButtons
OL,7,FAn NHS trust has removed advice from
OL,8,Fits website to give items such as
OL,9,FWotsists, Skips and Cadbury Buttons as
OL,10,Fto children learning to eat.
OL,12,FGateshead Health NHS Foundation Trust
OL,13,Fhad listed the items under a section
OL,14,Ftitled 'Bite and Dissolve' for
OL,15,Fchildren "struggling to accept lumps
OL,16,Fin food".
OL,1,W~k4~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}        G1/8
OL,2,W/*%+, "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNE Eng NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,423,420,120,260,000,100
PN,42202
SC,0002
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F422A1776856004
OL,3,CNHS trust removes advice to give
OL,4,Cchildren Wotsits, Skips and Cadbury
OL,5,CButtons
OL,7,FThe list, which did warn parents of
OL,8,Fthe high fat and sugar content,
OL,9,Fincluded Wotsits, Skips, Pom Bear
OL,10,Fcrisps, ice cream wafers, Cadbury
OL,11,FButtons and prawn crackers.
OL,13,FIn a Substack by British food writer
OL,14,Fand journalist Bee Wilson, she
OL,15,Fcondemned the advice, writing: "NHS
OL,16,FGateshead seems to be saying that if
OL,17,Fyou want your child to learn how to
OL,18,Feat actual real vegetables and eggs
OL,19,Fand lentils and fish, they first have
OL,20,Fto learn how to eat Quavers, Pom Bears
OL,21,Fand chocolate buttons."
OL,1,W~k4~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}        G2/8
OL,2,W/*%+, "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNE Eng NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,423,420,120,260,000,100
PN,42203
SC,0003
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F422A1776856004
OL,3,CNHS trust removes advice to give
OL,4,Cchildren Wotsits, Skips and Cadbury
OL,5,CButtons
OL,7,FA spokesperson for Gateshead Health
OL,8,FNHS Foundation Trust told ITV News
OL,9,FTyne Tees on Tuesday (21 April) that
OL,10,Fthe information was "not intended as
OL,11,Fgeneral dietary advice".
OL,13,FShe said: "We are aware of the
OL,14,Fconcerns raised about information
OL,15,Fpreviously published on our website
OL,16,Frelating to food textures for young
OL,17,Fchildren.
OL,1,W~k4~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}        G3/8
OL,2,W/*%+, "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNE Eng NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,423,420,120,260,000,100
PN,42204
SC,0004
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F422A1776856004
OL,3,CNHS trust removes advice to give
OL,4,Cchildren Wotsits, Skips and Cadbury
OL,5,CButtons
OL,7,F"The content came from a patient
OL,8,Fleaflet developed with clinical input
OL,9,Fto support children with specific
OL,10,Fswallowing or feeding difficulties who
OL,11,Fneed help to manage different textures
OL,12,Fsafely.
OL,14,F"It was not intended as general
OL,15,Fdietary advice. The foods referenced
OL,16,Fwere provided as examples of textures
OL,17,Fthat dissolve easily in the mouth, not
OL,18,Frecommendations about what children
OL,19,Fshould routinely eat."
OL,1,W~k4~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}        G4/8
OL,2,W/*%+, "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNE Eng NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,423,420,120,260,000,100
PN,42205
SC,0005
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F422A1776856004
OL,3,CNHS trust removes advice to give
OL,4,Cchildren Wotsits, Skips and Cadbury
OL,5,CButtons
OL,7,FThe trust has now removed the 'Bite
OL,8,Fand Dissolve' section, and in its
OL,9,Fplace it says: "This section is
OL,10,Fcurrently being reviewed and will be
OL,11,Fupdated soon.
OL,13,F"In the meantime, parents and carers
OL,14,Fshould always follow advice from their
OL,15,Fhealth visitor or clinical team if
OL,16,Fthey have concerns about feeding their
OL,17,Fchild."
OL,1,W~k4~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}        G5/8
OL,2,W/*%+, "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,,,
